{"tid":358862,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple 修改退貨政策 8月15日起 網上商店將不予退貨","createTime":"2017-08-14T04:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T17:00:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc936fa9d8388e39131d4aa26f5fe369eabe7318","tid":358862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"每年 iPhone 新型號推出，都會有一番搶購潮，其中有不少人都是買來炒賣圖利。最近 Apple 就決定修改網上商店的條款，列明在網上商店購買的產品將不能退貨。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Apple 網上商店的退貨政策是，貨品售出後 14 日內可以退貨，但需要收取機價 15% 的退貨費用。不過在官方網頁上，最近就出現了一個新提示，表示退貨政策將於 2017 年 8 月 15 日起修改，而當日之後提交的訂單將適用新政策。如果在網上商店購買 iPhone，更直接標明新政策就是不接受退貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/08/13/apple-aos-no-refund/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2Fapple-aos-no-refund%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=i9CbHxcJtuCueviEpLrmVTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2582c0f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/08/13/apple-aos-no-refund/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"482791b9d9dec7b423b49f2e536c633a2c6afca0","tid":358862,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:24:39.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ab8ab9fd30e29549ccd1ce30a18ea6fc565c11","tid":358862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。<br />\n只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。<br />\n只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。<br />\n只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。<br />\n只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。</span>"},{"pid":"53a2123bfcfaaae52c9a5501e340fc3109b07536","tid":358862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"Apple HK：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNo Service<br />\nNo Repair（外判 街邊工人）<br />\nNo refund<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=